metadata.name: The Disciple
metadata.description:
Rekindle dreams of the past, embrace your haunting lament. 

Your challenge and hardship has shattered into growth and admission.

No malevolent glare that can curse the wistful presence from eyes that reflect actions and discussion.

Preservation in these depths, in the chaos and in the eerie moments of roaring solitude.
